Any commit (revision) can be tagged:
git tag tag_name    -   tags current version with 'tag_name'
git tag tag_name 9fceb02    -   tags a commit with sha 9fceb02

Show all tags:
git tag

Show current version tags:
git tag --points-at HEAD

Tags are not automatically pushed with 'git push', so you have to push it manually:
git push origin tag_name

To checkout to a version marked with some tag:
git checkout tag_name
